; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.004) 1px 1px 1px; width: 1615px; height: 194px; line-height: 194px; top: 10067px; left: 1620px; z-index: 363;">解决浏览器兼容性问题</p><p class="reader-word-layer reader-word-s2-9" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 160px; font-weight: 600; font-family: simsun; position: absolute; word-break: keep-all; white-space: nowrap; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.004) 1px 1px 1px; width: 54px; height: 194px; line-height: 194px; top: 10067px; left: 3237px; z-index: 366;">&nbsp;</p><p class="reader-word-layer reader-word-s2-24" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, a600700e650e52ea551898540020002, Verdana; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 160px; letter-spacing: 0.36px; position: absolute; word-break: keep-all; white-space: nowrap; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.004) 1px 1px 1px; width: 788px; height: 194px; line-height: 194px; top: 10577px; left: 1448px; z-index: 367;">javascript</p><p class="reader-word-layer reader-word-s2-2 reader-word-s2-16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 160px; font-family: 宋体, a600700e650e52ea551898540040002, 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.35px; position: absolute; word-break: keep-all; white-space: nowrap; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.004) 1px 1px 1px; width: 2409px; height: 194px; line-height: 194px; top: 10577px; left: 2278px; z-index: 368;">脚本在不同浏览器的兼容性一直是</p><p class="reader-word-layer reader-word-s2-0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, a600700e650e52ea551898540020002, Verdana; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 160px; position: absolute; word-break: keep-all; white-space: nowrap; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.004) 1px 1px 1px; width: 354px; height: 194px;